    "original": "Having just landed a hit, this character is ready to perform a powerful followup strike! The next attack will inflict [color=",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"Having just landed a hit, this character is ready to perform a powerful followup strike! The next attack will inflict [color=\" + this.Const.UI.Color.PositiveValue + \"]+20%[/color] damage to a single target. If multiple targets are hit, only the first one will receive increased damage. If the attack misses, the effect is wasted.\""
